OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry. Patchy mist and low cloud in
OL,9,Fcentral and eastern areas.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAny overnight mist and low
OL,12,Fcloud soon clearing to leave a dry day
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Becoming warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAll
OL,16,Fparts remaining dry and settled into
OL,17,Fthe weekend with plenty of warm
OL,18,Fsunshine, but likely a bit cloudier on
OL,19,FSunday. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
